[color=RoyalBlue][head=2]Employment Agreement[/head][/color]

[bold]Applicant,[/bold] by filling out this application, you agree to follow the orders of your department head as they relate to your duties and position in the department. Furthermore, you accept the obligations and responsibilities you will have to your department of employment, and declare your willingness to contribute to the success of your department, and the station as a whole.

[bold]Department Head,[/bold] by stamping this application, you agree that the applicant is suitable to the environment of your department, and that they show sufficient understanding and willingness to be able to enter a learning position in the department. You certify that you are willing to instruct the applicant of their duties to your department, and provide guidance and orders that contribute to their success, and the success of the station.

[bold]Head of Personnel,[/bold] by stamping this application, you agree that the applicant's position in this department will uphold the obligations and responsibilities that the applicant has to the station, and that the applicant is suitable to be an employee of the department they applied for. Additionally, you certify that the applicant understands the position they are applying for, and the opportunities that they will have in the department they are joining.

[bold]Priority Acceptance[/bold]
Applicants who have previously signed a Release Agreement to resign from the department they are now applying for have Priority Acceptance, means that the Head of Personnel can approve a Job Application for the individual to their department without further needing approval from either the Head of the Department or from the Captain.

[color=RoyalBlue]──────────────────────────────────────[/color]

[color=Gray]Ensure all information on this application is accurate to the greatest extent of your knowledge. After finishing the application, submit this form to the Head of Personnel for review. Your application might take some time to be processed, please be patient as this occurs. An approved application is only valid if stamped by the Head of Personnel and either the related Department Head or the Captain. A Central Command stamp can also validate this form.[/color]
